OL,3,CGrandmother suffers broken wrist and
OL,4,Cfractured ribs in e-bike crash
OL,6,FA grandmother says she was left in
OL,7,F"terrible" pain having suffered a
OL,8,Fbroken wrist and fractured ribs when
OL,9,Fshe was hit by an electric bike.
OL,11,FChristina Marchand, 75, was struck as
OL,12,Fshe walked along the pavement to her
OL,13,Flocal shop in Brighton, Sussex.
OL,15,FA teenager was riding the electric
OL,16,Fbike illegally along the pavement,
OL,17,Fwhich can lead to a #30 fine.
OL,19,FChristina says the rider claimed they
OL,20,Fwere unable to stop, but it has left
OL,21,Fher concerned for her safety.
