OL,6,FChristina said: "It makes me angry
OL,7,Fbecause I see them all the time on the
OL,8,Fpavement. But you just don't see them
OL,9,Fcoming and you don't hear them so it's
OL,10,Fterrible really."
OL,12,FAfter the incident, Christina says she
OL,13,F"couldn't really do anything" for
OL,14,Fherself and had to stay with her son.
OL,16,FChristina's son-in-law, Mohammed
OL,17,FMahsin, runs a cafe along Whitehawk
OL,18,FRoad, near to where the incident took
OL,19,Fplace. As soon as he heard what had
OL,20,Fhappened, he rushed over.
