OL,6,FMohammed said: "I said, okay, I'm
OL,7,Fcoming. So I straightaway went there
OL,8,Fand she was on the floor in pain and
OL,9,Fagony."
OL,11,FChristina has been told it will take
OL,12,Faround six weeks for her injuries to
OL,13,Fheal.
OL,15,FElectric bikes and electric scooters,
OL,16,Falso known as e-bikes and e-scooters,
OL,17,Fare becoming increasingly popular.
