OL,6,FThere are currently 104 bike hire hubs
OL,7,Facross Brighton and Hove consisting of
OL,8,F780 bikes, with 60% being e-bikes and
OL,9,F40% being pedal-only bikes.
OL,11,FIn the last 18 months in the city,
OL,12,Fmore than 1.2 million kilometres have
OL,13,Fbeen travelled by users in over
OL,14,F400,000 journeys.
OL,16,FCurrently, privately owned e-scooters
OL,17,Fare not allowed to be used on public
OL,18,Froads, pavements or in cycle lanes.
