OL,6,FThe Transport Secretary, Louise Haigh,
OL,7,Fhas indicated that the Government
OL,8,Fintends to legalise the use of private
OL,9,Fe-scooters on roads so they can be
OL,10,Fregulated.
OL,12,FLouise Haigh MP, Transport Secretary,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We've not got parliamentary
OL,14,Ftime in this session or a relevant
OL,15,Fbill that could be used to regulate e-
OL,16,Fscooters, but we will we will look to
OL,17,Flegislate, absolutely it's clearly
OL,18,Frequired.
OL,20,F"It's not good enough that it's been
OL,21,Fleft in this situation for too long."
