OL,6,FCllr Trevor Muten, Cabinet Member for
OL,7,FTransport, Parking and Public Realm,
OL,8,FBrighton and Hove City Council, said:
OL,9,F"We're very sorry to hear this
OL,10,Fresident has been injured and we will
OL,11,Fbe looking into the incident with
OL,12,FBeryl.
OL,14,F"We are committed to doing all we can
OL,15,Fto promote safe and responsible
OL,16,Fcycling throughout the city but do
OL,17,Fexpect everyone who hires a Beryl Bike
OL,18,Fto ride them responsibly and obey the
OL,19,FHighway Code."
