OL,6,FIn a statement, Sussex Police said:
OL,7,F"We received a report of a collision
OL,8,Finvolving an e-bike and a pedestrian
OL,9,Fin Whitehawk Road, Brighton, at about
OL,10,F5.15pm on October 19. The pedestrian,
OL,11,Fa 75-year-old woman, sustained
OL,12,Finjuries.
OL,14,F"Officers are investigating and have
OL,15,Fmade contact with her to share
OL,16,Fupdates, and to complete a welfare
OL,17,Fcheck.
